Package com.jaunt

Jaunt 0.9.7 [website] is a web-scraping & automation API that exposes a lighweight HTTP useragent (headless browser).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
FilterCallback An interface that defines callback methods used for filtering while parsing.
HeaderListener An interface that defines callback methods related to HTTP header activity.
 

Class Summary
Comment Represents an HTML/XHTML comment, CDATA section, DOCTYPE declaration, or processing instruction.
Cookie Represents a cookie.
CookieJar A container for Cookie objects.
Document Represents an HTML, XHTML, or XML Document
Element This class represents an HTML, XHTML, or XML Element.
Elements A container class for holding search results, which is itself searchable (inheriting search methods from Element).
Filter Default implementation of FilterCallback that allows everything through the filter.
HttpRequest Represents an Http request.
HttpResponse This class encapsulates summary information of an HTTP response.
Node Represents a Node in the DOM.
Text Represents a text node in the DOM.
UserAgent UserAgent class represents a lightweight, headless browser for XML, XHTML and XML documents.
UserAgentSettings Represents UserAgent settings.
 

Exception Summary
JauntException Represents a Jaunt related error.
MultipleFound Represents an error caused by an finding multiple instances of an object when only one was anticipated.
NodeNotFound Represents an error caused by an inability to find a Node.
NotFound Represents an error caused by an inability to locate the target of a search.
ResponseException Represents a connection error or HTTP error.
SearchException Represents an error related to a search function.

Jaunt 0.9.7 [website] is a web-scraping & automation API that exposes a lighweight HTTP useragent (headless browser).
